      "type": "paragraph",
      "id": "0eb93b51-e145-40bc-94ec-3bba14e48d05",
      "text": "Holacracy is a specific social technology or system of organizational governance developed by HolacracyOne, LLC in which authority and decision-making are distributed throughout a holarchy of self-organizing teams rather than being vested in a management hierarchy. Holacracy has been adopted in for-profit and non-profit organizations in Australia, France, Germany, New Zealand, Switzerland, the United Kingdom, and the United States - [https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Holacracy wikipedia]"
